:formula_3

Here is the expected value of .

Note that the inequalities also hold when the have been obtained using sampling without replacement; in this case the random variables are not independent anymore. A proof of this statement can be found in Hoeffding&#x27;s paper. For slightly better bounds in the case of sampling without replacement, see for instance the paper by .

