<doc id="1136367" wikidata="Q5448352" url="?curid=1136367" title="File on 4">
<text>File on 4 is a current-affairs radio programme produced by BBC News and broadcast on BBC Radio 4. First broadcast from Manchester in 1977, it is produced in Salford by the BBC&#x27;s Radio Current Affairs department. It has won more than forty awards, including a gold Sony Radio Award in 2003.

